                                                    ~*~ SweetEscape Airlines ~*~

Welcome to SweetEscape Airlines! We hope each traveler has a pleasant trip no matter where they are going!
For your trip we need to know some information on who you are, where you want to travel to and from, and if you are a member. Let's get started!

1) Make a profile, enter your personal details
2) Pick flight with its according cabin information
3) Save your ticket in a proper place as it will be your boarding pass

